title: Viral video: Star Wars, Drake dancing and Britney's broken zip
text: Viral video: Star Wars, Drake dancing and Britney's broken zip Friday, 23 October 2015 (21 minutes ago) Spears suffers a wardrobe malfunction, Tom Hiddleston channels Hank Williams and a message from Back to the Future’s Doc Brown Zip me baby, one more time – that’s the plea from Britney Spears as she suffers a wardrobe malfunction during a performance in Las Vegas. The singer’s zip broke on the back of her costume ...
